00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:13.280
 Dr. Shrashidele, Happy New Year! This is the starting Tibetan Royal Era, 2,140, and so

00:00:13.280 --> 00:00:20.240
 I'm very happy to celebrate of these beautiful opportunities. New Year always reminds of the

00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:26.480
 beautiful lives that we went through, and here we are again. And so I'm very happy to everyone

00:00:26.480 --> 00:00:34.480
 to greet, and I wish you happy, healthy, and long life, joy and peace, happiness,

00:00:34.480 --> 00:00:40.560
 and fulfillment of every beautiful aspirations that you are desiring in your heart, and continue

00:00:40.560 --> 00:00:46.480
 for that. And this is again, New Year is one of the celebrations of our lives that we will

00:00:46.480 --> 00:00:54.320
 continue moving forward. So we should always remember how the precious life is, and how

00:00:54.320 --> 00:01:00.480
 beautiful it is, and how we're going to take care of this beautiful precious life, and lives

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:07.200
 of others that we are connected. So continue to help and support our capabilities, which is the

00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:13.040
 whole mark, the essential teaching of the Buddha Shakyamuni, and Guru Padmasambha also. Again,

00:01:13.040 --> 00:01:21.200
 we stand in our every beautiful aspirations and wish that we like to prefer and then move forward.

00:01:21.200 --> 00:01:25.920
 And for that very reason, I'd like to do short prayers on these beautiful occasions.

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:30.400
 Pray to the three dual, Buddha Dharmasanga, Guru Padmasambha,

00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:36.240
 Buddha Shakyamuni, as well as Tara, and all enlightened beings.

